%% Diagram: Choosing a CRDT variant
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Need a CRDT] --> B{Reliable causal<br/>delivery available?}
    B -->|No| C{State size bounded?}
    B -->|Yes| D{Bandwidth budget?}
    C -->|Yes| E[State-based<br/>CvRDT]
    C -->|No| F[Delta-state]
    D -->|Tight| G[Operation-based<br/>CmRDT]
    D -->|Generous| F
    E --> H[Gossip OK,<br/>any order]
    F --> I[Track sync<br/>vector per peer]
    G --> J[Invest in causal<br/>broadcast layer]
